关于Kali 2.0装中文输入法的问题 

首先要添加更新源

deb http://security.kali.org/kali-security/ sana/updates main contrib non-free
deb-src http://security.kali.org/kali-security/ sana/updates main contrib non-free



deb http://mirrors.aliyun.com/kali kali main non-free contrib
deb-src http://mirrors.aliyun.com/kali kali main non-free contrib
deb http://mirrors.aliyun.com/kali-security kali/updates main contrib non-free

deb http://http.kali.org/kali kali main non-free contribdeb-src 
deb http://http.kali.org/kali kali main non-free contribdeb 
deb http://security.kali.org/kali-security kali/updates main contrib non-free

deb http://repo.kali.org/kali kali-bleeding-edge maindeb-src 
deb http://repo.kali.org/kali kali-bleeding-edge main

deb http://mirrors.ustc.edu.cn/kali kali main non-free contribdeb-src 
deb http://mirrors.ustc.edu.cn/kali kali main non-free contribdeb 
deb http://mirrors.ustc.edu.cn/kali-security kali/updates main contrib non-free

deb http://mirrors.aliyun.com/kali kali main non-free contribdeb-src 
deb http://mirrors.aliyun.com/kali kali main non-free contribdeb 
deb http://mirrors.aliyun.com/kali-security kali/updates main contrib non-free

leafpad /etc/apt/sources.list  直接复制可以不需要用VIM 打开就是记事本

apt-get update

apt-get upgrade

apt-get install fcitx fcitx-googlepinyin		//谷歌输入法

reboot  										//重启


